  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2565450/extras/bde7207b1d26afb4fbfc350f42c44f7b.avif?t=1709938254\" width=582 height=102 /></span><br><br>Greebles is an action packed game of skill involving bulldozers, cockroaches and fish. Players attempt to navigate a maze of blocks while crushing Greebles to gain points. The more Greebles you crush, the more points you get! Just don't let them touch you!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Key Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> 100 different levels with unique blocks, greebles, and specials. <br></li><li> Local PvP or Co-op with up to 4 players.<br></li><li> Multiplayer matches with up to 36 players.<br></li><li> 3 difficulty levels.</li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >How to Play</h2><br>Push blocks to send them sliding, time it right to scoop up greebles and crush them:<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2565450/extras/c1edd009b8ea6c7a18c5828239b17eed.poster.avif?t=1709938254\" width=360 height=120 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2565450/extras/c1edd009b8ea6c7a18c5828239b17eed.webm?t=1709938254\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2565450/extras/c1edd009b8ea6c7a18c5828239b17eed.mp4?t=1709938254\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Push a block that can't move to crush it. Some blocks grant buffs to the player, like speed:<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2565450/extras/a83075567f1e55a0a84f500cb4005cad.poster.avif?t=1709938254\" width=360 height=120 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2565450/extras/a83075567f1e55a0a84f500cb4005cad.webm?t=1709938254\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2565450/extras/a83075567f1e55a0a84f500cb4005cad.mp4?t=1709938254\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Be careful though, different types of blocks behave differently than regular blocks. Grenade blocks explode, pushing adjacent blocks and killing adjacent players or greebles:<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2565450/extras/68c0a4bf958f4307084a95e4e91591a4.poster.avif?t=1709938254\" width=360 height=120 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2565450/extras/68c0a4bf958f4307084a95e4e91591a4.webm?t=1709938254\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2565450/extras/68c0a4bf958f4307084a95e4e91591a4.mp4?t=1709938254\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Bounce blocks prevent blocks from stopping when they otherwise would, and generator blocks can't be pushed, but periodically spawn new greebles:<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2565450/extras/a0ebbe5b89b28ee76debdb1272db0f37.poster.avif?t=1709938254\" width=360 height=120 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2565450/extras/a0ebbe5b89b28ee76debdb1272db0f37.webm?t=1709938254\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2565450/extras/a0ebbe5b89b28ee76debdb1272db0f37.mp4?t=1709938254\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Some generators can be crushed, others can only be destroyed by surrounding them with blocks.<br><br>Gameplay progresses to the next level when all greebles and greeble generators have been destroyed. <br><br>There are many other types of blocks, here are just a few:<br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Shield - protects you from greebles and sliding blocks.<br></li><li> Freeze - slows other players, and stops greebles in their tracks.<br></li><li> Bonus - crush these for extra points.<br></li><li> Fireball - grants the ability to launch grenade blocks.<br></li><li> Death Touch - protects you from greebles, and kills anything you touch.</li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Multiplayer</h2><br>While fun to play solo, Greebles becomes much more fun with friends. Up to 4 players can play (PvP or co-op) on a single machine, although it can get a bit crowded around the keyboard! Up to 9 machines (any platform) can connect for LAN play, for a total limit of 36 players per match!<br><br><br>Available natively on Windows, macOS, and Linux. Greebles intends to be an exact replica of the original game released in 1997. (Produced in collaboration with Stairways Software)",
  "about_the_game": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2565450/extras/bde7207b1d26afb4fbfc350f42c44f7b.avif?t=1709938254\" width=582 height=102 /></span><br><br>Greebles is an action packed game of skill involving bulldozers, cockroaches and fish. Players attempt to navigate a maze of blocks while crushing Greebles to gain points. The more Greebles you crush, the more points you get! Just don't let them touch you!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Key Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> 100 different levels with unique blocks, greebles, and specials. <br></li><li> Local PvP or Co-op with up to 4 players.<br></li><li> Multiplayer matches with up to 36 players.<br></li><li> 3 difficulty levels.</li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >How to Play</h2><br>Push blocks to send them sliding, time it right to scoop up greebles and crush them:<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2565450/extras/c1edd009b8ea6c7a18c5828239b17eed.poster.avif?t=1709938254\" width=360 height=120 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2565450/extras/c1edd009b8ea6c7a18c5828239b17eed.webm?t=1709938254\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2565450/extras/c1edd009b8ea6c7a18c5828239b17eed.mp4?t=1709938254\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Push a block that can't move to crush it. Some blocks grant buffs to the player, like speed:<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2565450/extras/a83075567f1e55a0a84f500cb4005cad.poster.avif?t=1709938254\" width=360 height=120 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2565450/extras/a83075567f1e55a0a84f500cb4005cad.webm?t=1709938254\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2565450/extras/a83075567f1e55a0a84f500cb4005cad.mp4?t=1709938254\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Be careful though, different types of blocks behave differently than regular blocks. Grenade blocks explode, pushing adjacent blocks and killing adjacent players or greebles:<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2565450/extras/68c0a4bf958f4307084a95e4e91591a4.poster.avif?t=1709938254\" width=360 height=120 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2565450/extras/68c0a4bf958f4307084a95e4e91591a4.webm?t=1709938254\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2565450/extras/68c0a4bf958f4307084a95e4e91591a4.mp4?t=1709938254\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Bounce blocks prevent blocks from stopping when they otherwise would, and generator blocks can't be pushed, but periodically spawn new greebles:<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2565450/extras/a0ebbe5b89b28ee76debdb1272db0f37.poster.avif?t=1709938254\" width=360 height=120 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2565450/extras/a0ebbe5b89b28ee76debdb1272db0f37.webm?t=1709938254\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2565450/extras/a0ebbe5b89b28ee76debdb1272db0f37.mp4?t=1709938254\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Some generators can be crushed, others can only be destroyed by surrounding them with blocks.<br><br>Gameplay progresses to the next level when all greebles and greeble generators have been destroyed. <br><br>There are many other types of blocks, here are just a few:<br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Shield - protects you from greebles and sliding blocks.<br></li><li> Freeze - slows other players, and stops greebles in their tracks.<br></li><li> Bonus - crush these for extra points.<br></li><li> Fireball - grants the ability to launch grenade blocks.<br></li><li> Death Touch - protects you from greebles, and kills anything you touch.</li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Multiplayer</h2><br>While fun to play solo, Greebles becomes much more fun with friends. Up to 4 players can play (PvP or co-op) on a single machine, although it can get a bit crowded around the keyboard! Up to 9 machines (any platform) can connect for LAN play, for a total limit of 36 players per match!<br><br><br>Available natively on Windows, macOS, and Linux. Greebles intends to be an exact replica of the original game released in 1997. (Produced in collaboration with Stairways Software)",
